    <item>
      <title>美国财产损失导致日本青空银行股价下跌 20%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/aozora-plunges-20-after-bank-forecasts-loss-on-us-property</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本青空银行(Aozora Bank Ltd.)成为数小时内第二家因与美国商业地产相关的损失而令投资者大吃一惊的银行，导致其股价跌停，并加剧了人们对全球银行面临的房地产投资恶化风险的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-01/aozora-plunges-20-after-bank-forecasts-loss-on-us-property</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 01:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
